# Environment Configuration

## Development (.env.development)
```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000
VITE_LOG_LEVEL=DEBUG
```

## Production (.env.production)
```
VITE_API_URL=https://api.example.com
VITE_LOG_LEVEL=ERROR
```

